SUMMARY:Women’s History Celebration at Breathless Wines
DESCRIPTION:Women’s History Celebration Sundays at Breathless Wines are held on Sundays\, Mar 1st - 29th form 12–2 p.m.\, honoring Women’s History Month and the theme from the National Women's History Alliance\, “Leading the Change: Women Shaping a Sustainable Future.” The series celebrates women driving environmental\, economic\, and social innovation through leadership and community impact. Each luncheon pairs a featured speaker with sparkling wines and a meal prepared by Chef Beryl Adler of Acorn Café\, creating an inspiring afternoon of conversation and connection in the winery’s garden setting. 
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/womens-history-celebration-sundays-at-breathless-wines/
LOCATION:499 Moore Ln, Healdsburg, CA, 95448, United States
GEO:-122.876547;38.612931
