SUMMARY:Italian Brunch Series at Seghesio Family Vineyards
DESCRIPTION:Experience the Italian Brunch Series at Seghesio Family Vineyards\, inspired by the family’s deep Italian roots and tradition. This inviting gathering celebrates fresh flavors\, warm hospitality\, and the joy of sharing a meal around the table.    Guests are welcomed to a relaxed brunch experience filled with laughter\, abundant dishes\, and thoughtfully paired wines. Enjoy beautiful pairings featuring Seghesio favorites such as crisp Vermentino\, vibrant Barbera\, and soulful Sangiovese each adding to the spirit of an Italian-inspired welcome.    Dates include February 15\, March 15\, May 3\, and September 20 for a special Harvest Edition. Includes a $25 Wine Credit with $100 wine purchase.    
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/italian-brunch-series-at-seghesio-family-vineyards-2026-03-15/
LOCATION:700 Grove Street, Healdsburg, CA, 95448, United States
GEO:-122.874984;38.6179675
